  "detailed_description": "Blockpop heroes is a minimalist fun runner, based primarily on jumps rather than distance, which parodies pop culture heroes through the appearance of \"blocks\" and a simple and wacky story.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Quick and easy gameplay, no hassle!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Jump and jump again to unlock over 50 characters!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each jump makes a random sound from over 20 possible intonations, each level will have a different composition! </li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Original boss fights!</li></ul>",
